+/**
+ * Analytics aggregation service — processes raw order and user data
+ * into analytics summaries for the dashboard.
+ *
+ * Depends on:
+ * - OrderRepository (data layer) for order data
+ * - UserRepository (data layer) for user data
+ *
+ * Architecture note: This service performs read-only aggregation over
+ * existing repository data. It does not maintain its own data store.
+ */
